com.microblink.entities.parsers.config.randomfield

Class RandomFieldBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • com.microblink.entities.parsers.config.randomfield.RandomFieldBundle

  • public final class RandomFieldBundle
extends <any>
    Represents a bundle of RandomFieldElement objects which are grouped to one or multiple RandomFieldElementGroup groups that can travel via Intent. Used inside RandomFieldUISettings which is used by RandomFieldOverlayController and RandomFieldScanActivity.
